Package: SPAC
Type: Package
Title: A flexible copula-based approach for the analysis of secondary phenotypes in ascertained samples
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: c(person("Karim", "Oualkacha", email =
             "oualkacha.karim@uqam.ca", role = c("aut", "cre")),
             person("Geneviève", "Lefebvre", email =
